"{\"uid\": \"messengernews.net-news-news-brief-2024-08-fd-is-tops-in-special-olympics-donations\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Aug 24, 2024  Fort Dodge won the gold medal in the recent Special Olympics Iowa Cop on a Rooftop fundraiser.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 108, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 14, \"end\": 24, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fort_Dodge,_Iowa\", \"score\": 0.9830306005240314, \"rank\": 0.011996690568121058, \"text\": \"Fort Dodge\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fort_Dodge,_Iowa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fort_Dodge,_Iowa\"}, {\"begin\": 58, \"end\": 74, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Special_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.70490454317763e-16, \"text\": \"Special Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Special_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Special_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 75, \"end\": 79, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iowa\", \"score\": 0.9999999051124223, \"rank\": 9.488531472972577e-08, \"text\": \"Iowa\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iowa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iowa\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The city Police Department was recently informed that Fort Dodge was the No.\", \"from\": 110, \"to\": 186, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 119, \"end\": 136, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Metropolitan_Police_Department_of_the_District_of_Columbia\", \"score\": 0.4295771876044987, \"rank\": 0.8174628201014447, \"text\": \"Police Department\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Metropolitan_Police_Department_of_the_District_of_Columbia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Metropolitan_Police_Department_of_the_District_of_Columbia\"}, {\"begin\": 164, \"end\": 174, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fort_Dodge,_Iowa\", \"score\": 0.9830306005240314, \"rank\": 0.011996690568121058, \"text\": \"Fort Dodge\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fort_Dodge,_Iowa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fort_Dodge,_Iowa\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"1 fundraising location in Iowa this year.\", \"from\": 187, \"to\": 228, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 213, \"end\": 217, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iowa\", \"score\": 0.9999999051124223, \"rank\": 9.488531472972577e-08, \"text\": \"Iowa\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iowa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iowa\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Area residents donated $3,137.02 to Special Olympics Iowa during the Aug. 16 event at Dunkin', 2520 Fifth Ave. S.  Personnel from the Fort Dodge Police Department, Webster County Sheriff's Office and the Fort Dodge Correctional Facility were at the shop from 6 a.m. to noon that day to collect the donations.\", \"from\": 230, \"to\": 538, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 316, \"end\": 323, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dunkin'_Donuts\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Dunkin'\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dunkin'_Donuts\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dunkin'_Donuts\"}, {\"begin\": 364, \"end\": 374, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fort_Dodge,_Iowa\", \"score\": 0.9830306005240314, \"rank\": 0.011996690568121058, \"text\": \"Fort Dodge\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fort_Dodge,_Iowa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fort_Dodge,_Iowa\"}, {\"begin\": 375, \"end\": 392, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Metropolitan_Police_Department_of_the_District_of_Columbia\", \"score\": 0.4295771876044987, \"rank\": 0.8174628201014447, \"text\": \"Police Department\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Metropolitan_Police_Department_of_the_District_of_Columbia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/r